>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>**HTML <code>&lt;article&gt;</code>**元素表示文档、页面、应用或网站中的独立结构，其意在成为可独立分配的或可复用的结构，如在发布中，它可能是论坛帖子、杂志或新闻文章、博客、用户提交的评论、交互式组件，或者其他独立的内容项目。​​</p><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"445\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/tabbed/article.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>\n<p>给定文档中可以包含多篇文章;例如，阅读器在博客上滚动时一个接一个地显示每篇文章的文本，每个帖子将包含在<code>&lt;article&gt;</code>元素中，可能包含一个或多个<code>&lt;section&gt;</code>。</p>\n<table class=\"properties\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\"><dfn><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">内容分类 (en-US)</a></dfn></th>\n      <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Flow content (en-US)</a>, sectioning content, palpable content.</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">允许的内容</th>\n      <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Flow content (en-US)</a>.</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\"><dfn>标记省略</dfn></th>\n      <td>不允许，开始标签和结束标签都不能省略。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">允许的父元素</th>\n      <td>所有接受 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Flow content (en-US)</a>的元素。注意<code>&lt;article&gt;</code>元素不能成为<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a>元素的子元素。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">允许的 ARIA roles</th>\n      <td><code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#application\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">application</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#document\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">document</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#feed\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">feed</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#main\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">main</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#presentation\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">presentation</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#region\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">region</a></code></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">DOM 实例</th>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<p>此元素只具有<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">全局属性 (en-US)</a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"使用说明","title":"使用说明","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>每个<code>&lt;article&gt;</code>，通常包括标题（&lt;h1&gt; - &lt;h6&gt;元素）作为<code>&lt;article&gt;</code>元素的子元素。</li>\n  <li>当<code>&lt;article&gt;</code>元素嵌套使用时，则该元素代表与外层元素有关的文章。例如，代表博客评论的<code>&lt;article&gt;</code>元素可嵌套在代表博客文章的<code>&lt;article&gt;</code>元素中。</li>\n  <li><code>&lt;article&gt;</code>元素的作者信息可通过<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a>元素提供，但是不适用于嵌套的<code>&lt;article&gt;</code>元素。</li>\n  <li><code>&lt;article&gt;</code>元素的发布日期和时间可通过<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a>元素的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time#attr-pubdate\"><code>pubdate</code></a>属性表示。</li>\n  <li>可以使用<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a> 元素的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time#attr-datetime\"><code>datetime</code></a>属性来描述<code>&lt;article&gt;</code>元素的发布日期和时间。请注意<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a>的*<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time#attr-pubdate\"><code>pubdate</code></a>* 属性不再是*<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/W3C\">W3C <small>(en-US)</small></a>* *<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/HTML5\">HTML5</a>*标准。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: plain notranslate\">&lt;article class=\"film_review\"&gt;\n  &lt;header&gt;\n    &lt;h2&gt;Jurassic Park&lt;/h2&gt;\n  &lt;/header&gt;\n  &lt;section class=\"main_review\"&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;Dinos were great!&lt;/p&gt;\n  &lt;/section&gt;\n  &lt;section class=\"user_reviews\"&gt;\n    &lt;article class=\"user_review\"&gt;\n      &lt;p&gt;Way too scary for me.&lt;/p&gt;\n      &lt;footer&gt;\n        &lt;p&gt;\n          Posted on\n          &lt;time datetime=\"2015-05-16 19:00\"&gt;May 16&lt;/time&gt;\n          by Lisa.\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n      &lt;/footer&gt;\n    &lt;/article&gt;\n    &lt;article class=\"user_review\"&gt;\n      &lt;p&gt;I agree, dinos are my favorite.&lt;/p&gt;\n      &lt;footer&gt;\n        &lt;p&gt;\n          Posted on\n          &lt;time datetime=\"2015-05-17 19:00\"&gt;May 17&lt;/time&gt;\n          by Tom.\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n      &lt;/footer&gt;\n    &lt;/article&gt;\n  &lt;/section&gt;\n  &lt;footer&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;\n      Posted on\n      &lt;time datetime=\"2015-05-15 19:00\"&gt;May 15&lt;/time&gt;\n      by Staff.\n    &lt;/p&gt;\n  &lt;/footer&gt;\n&lt;/article&gt;\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/sections.html#the-article-element","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"html.elements.article"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容","id":"浏览器兼容","isH3":false,"query":"html.elements.article","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关文章","title":"相关文章","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>Others section-related elements: <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/body\"><code>&lt;body&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/aside\"><code>&lt;aside&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h1&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h2&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h3&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h4&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h5&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h6&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/hgroup\"><code>&lt;hgroup&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/footer\"><code>&lt;footer&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Sections_and_Outlines_of_an_HTML5_document\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">Sections and outlines of an HTML5 document</a>.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"使用说明","id":"使用说明"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容","id":"浏览器兼容"},{"text":"相关文章","id":"相关文章"}],"summary":"**HTML <article>**元素表示文档、页面、应用或网站中的独立结构，其意在成为可独立分配的或可复用的结构，如在发布中，它可能是论坛帖子、杂志或新闻文章、博客、用户提交的评论、交互式组件，或者其他独立的内容项目。​​","popularity":0.0007,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<article>: The Article Contents element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"article","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<article> : l'élément de contenu d'un article","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<article>: 記事コンテンツ要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<article>","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"article (artigo)","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"<article>","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/html/element/article","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/html/element/article/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML（超文本标记语言）"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"HTML 元素参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article","title":"<article>"}],"pageTitle":"<article> - HTML（超文本标记语言） | MDN","noIndexing":false